  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Each set of clustered reads was then separately assembled using the ONT assembly method for isolates described in Section 2.6.",
    "The resulting phased assemblies were checked for quality with CheckM (Parks et al., 2015) as described in Section 2.4, and ARGs and resistance-conferring SNPs were analyzed using AMRFinderPlus as described in Section 2.4, with the additional \"-organism\" option set to the organism of interest to identify SNPs.",
    "Further manual inspection of SNPs was performed with SAMtools v1.17 (Danecek et al., 2021) and IGV (Thorvaldsdóttir et al., 2013).",
    "Illumina short-read sequencing data for E. coli isolates was generated, assembled and sequence typed as described in Ringenier et al.",
    "(under review), using a previously published STEC pipeline (v1.0, available at https://galaxy.sciensano.be; Bogaerts et al., 2021)."
  ],
